Jane Clifton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jane_Clifton 0 Jane Clifton (born 10 April 1949) is an Australian actress, singer, writer and voice artist. Clifton was born in Gibraltar to British Army parents. In 1961 she emigrated to Perth, Australia, before later settling in Melbourne. She became a naturalised citizen of Australia in 1992.
